moslem equivalent of the red cross said he opposed for tactical 
reasons making the concession of recognizing israel in advance of 
negotiations 
the matter of recognizing the jewish presence here is really 
no longer in question but how can i recognize israel when israel 
does not recongize me when israel claims all of palestinian to be 
their territory abdel shafi said 
he said he hoped the palestinian council would not take a 
decison until after israels nov 1 elections so as to not to make 
advance concessions 
it is not known which group commands the most support although 
the conventional wisdom is that islamic militants have the backing 
of most of gazas 650000 residents and fatah controls most of the 
west banks 850000 palestinians 
