regional coordinator thousands of smaller informal mars parties 
also will be held she said 
on saturday outerspace buffs were encouraged to bring mars 
bars and other earthly delights to a mars watch picnic and jazz 
concert at the college 
the last time earth and mars were so close was in 1971 warns 
said he said viewing conditions this time are better because the 
planet is much higher in the sky 
itll appear the brightest during september then itll get 
dimmer as the two planets move away he said 
