administrations economic record saying fridays unemployment 
figures showed that the jobless rate hovered just above the 
lowest its been in 14 years 
the figures from the labor department showed unemployment of 56 
percent up from 54 percent in july and from the may figure of 53 
per cent which was a 14year low 
