survive 
these are scenes from the aftermath of the ramstein air show a 
week ago when three italian jets collided during a stunt and one 
crashed into a huge crowd of spectators and exploded 
fiftyone people died 15 remain unaccounted for and more than 
160 are hospitalized 
within an hour after sundays crash volunteers set up a 
